description:
Ok here goes,  This is actually a torrent to download a torrent.  Why? because the subject torrent is almost 4MB.  Too big of a torrent fir TPB to accept.  Big torrent because of BIG amount of files.  About 24GB of building dem map poi fda hnr fpa etc for iGO.  This has multiple maps from Navteq TomTom and others for many regions.  A lot of these will overlap with the other igo torrents but I think this mega collection is worth it for the additional files beside the map and poi.  You can select 1 file or all files in your torrent client.  Rest assured that there are plenty of seeds but as always please seed back and do your part.  


Here are just a small samples of the latest maps in the subject torrent.  Note though that some of these maps are not the latest up to date ones esp the navteq ones so should still download the other packs. For the most complete collection, this and the other pack should all be downloaded and all folders merge together.
